<div class="hero"><h1>Skin</h1><p>Quick-reference dermatology conditions and red-flag prompts.</p></div>
<div class="grid">
<div class="tile"><h3>🧴 Eczema flare</h3><details><summary>Open guidance</summary><ul><li>Assess trigger pattern, infection signs, and severity.</li><li>Emollient optimisation + topical steroid ladder.</li><li>Check adherence and steroid-phobia barriers.</li><li>Escalate if extensive, infected, or poor control.</li></ul></details></div>
<div class="tile"><h3>🔥 Cellulitis</h3><details><summary>Open guidance</summary><ul><li>Warmth, erythema, tenderness, spreading margin.</li><li>Mark edge, consider systemic symptoms and comorbidity.</li><li>Oral antibiotics per pathway if uncomplicated.</li><li>Urgent escalation if sepsis concern/rapid progression.</li></ul></details></div>
<div class="tile"><h3>🌿 Contact dermatitis</h3><details><summary>Open guidance</summary><ul><li>Identify likely irritant/allergen exposure.</li><li>Avoidance strategy + barrier/skin-care advice.</li><li>Topical anti-inflammatory treatment when flared.</li><li>Consider patch-testing referral if recurrent/severe.</li></ul></details></div>
<div class="tile"><h3>🫧 Urticaria</h3><details><summary>Open guidance</summary><ul><li>Transient itchy weals ± angioedema assessment.</li><li>Non-sedating antihistamine first-line.</li><li>Trigger review: infection, meds, foods, stress.</li><li>Emergency pathway for airway/breathing compromise.</li></ul></details></div>
<div class="tile"><h3>🦠 Shingles</h3><details><summary>Open guidance</summary><ul><li>Dermatomal painful vesicular rash, unilateral pattern.</li><li>Antiviral window and pain management review.</li><li>Eye involvement is urgent same-day ophthalmology route.</li></ul></details></div>
<div class="tile"><h3>⚠️ Suspicious lesion</h3><details><summary>Open guidance</summary><ul><li>Use ABCDE/ugly duckling checks and change over time.</li><li>Document size, border, colour, symptoms, photo if policy allows.</li><li>Urgent suspected-cancer pathway when criteria met.</li></ul></details></div>
</div>
<p class="note">Follow local/NICE skin and urgent referral pathways for diagnosis and management thresholds.</p>
